# Project Structure

This project is a Docusaurus documentation site for the Don't Starve Together Vanilla API.

## Key Configuration Files

- [docusaurus.config.ts](mdc:dst-api-webdocs/dst-api-webdocs/docusaurus.config.ts) - Main configuration file that defines site settings, plugins, and theme options
- [sidebars.ts](mdc:dst-api-webdocs/dst-api-webdocs/sidebars.ts) - Defines the sidebar navigation structure for documentation
- [package.json](mdc:dst-api-webdocs/dst-api-webdocs/package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:dst-api-webdocs/dst-api-webdocs/tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration

## Core Directories

- `/docs` - Contains markdown documentation files
  - `/api-vanilla` - API documentation organized by module categories
  
- `/src` - Source code
  - `/pages` - React components for custom pages
  - `/css` - Custom CSS files

- `/static` - Static assets
  - `/img` - Images including logo and favicon

## Development Workflow

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm start

# Build the site
npm run build

# Test the production build locally
npm run serve

# Deploy to GitHub Pages
npm run deploy
```

